# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:13
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_0305dee2:

    # pc "Do you ever talk to your real dad?"
    pc "Falas alguma vez com o teu pai verdadeiro?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:15
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_3f50f500:

    # ss "Not really. He calls on my birthday sometimes when he remembers."
    ss "Na verdade, não. Ele liga-me no meu aniversário, às vezes, quando se lembra."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:16
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_b137dcc6:

    # ss "He and mom split up when I was four. And he's gone a little crazy since then - conspiracy nut who is constantly posting ridiculous memes online."
    ss "Ele e a mãe separaram-se quando eu tinha quatro anos. E ele ficou um pouco maluco desde então — um fanático por teorias da conspiração que está constantemente a publicar memes ridículos online."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:17
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_1827b67e:

    # ss "I don't really like him all that much, honestly."
    ss "Sinceramente, não gosto muito dele."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:18
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_bed6ad0f:

    # ss "And I'm glad he lives all the way across the country. I haven't seen him in like five years now."
    ss "E fico contente por ele viver do outro lado do país. Já não o vejo há uns cinco anos."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:19
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_97748ea9:

    # ss "As far as I'm concerned, your dad is my dad."
    ss "No que a mim diz respeito, o teu pai é o meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:20
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_2600d93d:

    # ss "He's treated me more like a daughter than my real dad ever did."
    ss "Ele tratou-me mais como uma filha do que o meu pai verdadeiro alguma vez fez."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:22
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_2ff4738e:

    # ss "I wish he were here."
    ss "Quem me dera que ele estivesse aqui."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:23
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_107f9102:

    # pc "We'll find him."
    pc "Vamos encontrá-lo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:24
translate portuguese suzypersonal1_3dff063d:

    # ss "I hope so."
    ss "Espero que sim."

